{
  "ID": "SHIPPLASMA",
  "Group": "",
  "Name": {
    "English": "CYCLOTRON BALLISTA",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "回旋加速弩炮",
    "TencentChinese": "回旋加速弩炮",
    "TraditionalChinese": "迴旋加速弩砲"
  },
  "NameLower": {
    "English": "Cyclotron Ballista",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "回旋加速弩炮",
    "TencentChinese": "回旋加速弩炮",
    "TraditionalChinese": "迴旋加速弩砲"
  },
  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Anti-Electronics Starship Weapon",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "反电子飞船武器",
    "TencentChinese": "非引导性飞船武器",
    "TraditionalChinese": "反電子太空船武器"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A powerful ship-to-ship weapon, flinging plasmatic balls of ionising radiation towards the selected target. These projectiles can <span class=\"name name-technology\">disable starship engines</span>, leaving the target vulnerable to attack from other weapons.<br><br>These charged particles are <span class=\"name name-stellar\">extremely effective</span> against starship <span class=\"name name-stellar\">shields</span>, and considerably weaker against the metal armour of a ship's hull.<br><br>Use <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> to change weapon mode. Press <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> to fire.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种强大的舰对舰武器，将电离辐射的等离子球体射向选定的目标。这些射弹可以<span class=\"name name-technology\">使飞船驱动器失效</span>，从而使目标更容易受到其他武器的攻击。<br><br>这些带电粒子对飞船的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">护盾</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">极为有效</span>，但是对船体的金属装甲破坏力较弱。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>变更武器模式。按下<span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span>发射。",
    "TencentChinese": "向前方目标发射充满粒子的巨大浓缩球，造成巨大伤害。非定向，且将继续沿弹道飞行直至撞击物体。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種強大的太空船作戰武器，可向選定的目標投擲離子化輻射電漿球。這些射彈可以<span class=\"name name-technology\">癱瘓太空船引擎</span>，讓目標暴露在其他武器的攻擊下。<br><br>這些充能粒子對付太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">防護罩</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">極為有效</span>，對付太空船船身的金屬裝甲則顯得弱勢許多。<br><br>使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 即可切換武器模式。按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 即可開火。"
  },
